## Escort Profile Pages (Strapi-Led)

### Target Metrics
- **Word count**: 300-500 words unique description
- Profile data from Strapi, content structure from template

### Required Sections

#### 1. Profile Hero
- High-quality photos (gallery)
- Name, tagline
- Key stats: Age, height, languages
- Availability status (real-time from Strapi)

#### 2. About [Name]
- Personal description (unique per escort)
- Personality highlights
- Experience/background where appropriate

#### 3. Services Offered
- From Strapi service tags
- Link to service detail pages

#### 4. Rates & Booking
- Clear pricing table
- Duration options
- Booking CTA

#### 5. Availability
- Real-time calendar or status from Strapi
- Location availability

#### 6. Reviews (If Available)
- Verified reviews only
- Schema markup for reviews

---

## Blog Posts

### Target Metrics
- **Word count**: 800-1500 words (informational)
- **Read time**: 3-5 minutes

### Required Sections

#### 1. Introduction
- Hook in first paragraph
- Clear statement of what reader will learn
- Author byline with credentials (EEAT)

#### 2. Main Content
- **Format**: H2/H3 structure with scannable sections
- Include relevant internal links
- Use bullet points for lists

#### 3. Key Takeaways
- Summary box or bullet list
- Highlighted for featured snippet potential

#### 4. Author Bio
- Short bio with expertise signals
- Link to author page if available

#### 5. Related Content
- 2-3 related articles
- Relevant service/location pages

